" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyPK8Kvv.jpg&h=4489a814&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"79918b5cd2a30551ac6856d0756cdba860a66e72","tid":1748444,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T16:32:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5603fb3b3c3309ce1345ace85f1dc44c6408994","tid":1748444,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T16:32:59.000Z","msg":"香港多對外大愛撚"},{"pid":"207c663ada69b807dbb44f0b46b2c473d0b7522e","tid":1748444,"uid":49247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"085158479e175ea556dd2a80a0051543dcfa591f","tid":1748444,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T16:26:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZsavXW5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZsavXW5.png&h=0e9cb247&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人真係好低賤<br />\n當年四川大地震 捐左200億<br />\n過幾年比蝗蟲屌 香港冇幫佢地 見唔到有錢 死撚開<br />\n<br />\n無國界醫生年年捐5億<br />\n香港出事死人 叫極都唔幫手 重要唔比人cut捐款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解香港人咁低賤？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T16:33:35.000Z","msg":"冇槍冇軍隊，自不然比人睇低，有錢都冇撚用"},{"pid":"778be81a43a111da6f0b8f119ec3e56d20e5363b","tid":1748444,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T16:33:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">［請廣傳］<br />\n和理非目前可以做到嘅事</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最迫切：聽日區選同我投票啊！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一.）強烈建議香港人<span style=\"color: red;\">即時停止再月捐所有喺今次革命奶共/ 無幫過香港人嘅NGO組織</span>，將啲錢用喺更加有用嘅地方上面，例如揸車接放學嘅油費、飯券、法庭訟費、醫療開支、FA嘅物資費用等等<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n奶共/ 無幫過香港人嘅NGO組織例子：<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: gold;\">宣明會</span><br />\n（2018善款超過9.1億）：有巴絲post CUT捐回覆，「oh好遺憾」<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: gold;\">無國界醫生</span><br />\n（2017總收入超5億）：有巴絲post非新聞稿答覆，達哥式回應（一直有mon住關注情況，屌你你mon到香港淪陷埋先出手不如）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">（無恥界醫生條熱線已廢，想cut捐款但又打唔通hotline，可以直接打去銀行或者網上銀行自己cut）</span><br />\n3. <span style=\"color: gold;\">樂施會</span><br />\n（2017總收入超2.5億）：無回應，平行時空<br />\n4. <span style=\"color: gold;\">奧比斯香港</span><br />\n（2018年總收入超2.1億）：無回應，平行時空<br />\n5. <span style=\"color: gold;\">UNICEF HK</span><br />\n（2017年總收入超1.7億）：無回應，平行時空<br />\n6. <span style=\"color: gold;\">Save the Children</span><br />\n （2017年總收入超1.6億）：無回應，平行時空<br />\n7. <span style=\"color: gold;\">香港紅十字會</span><br />\n（2017/18年總收入超1.4億）：18/8出咗份聲明，借世界人道主義日輕輕帶過呼籲各方克制，過去兩個多月動員逾800人次做電話熱線加現場支援<a href=\"https://www.redcross.org.hk/tc/press_room/press_release_2019/201908182.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.redcross.org.hk%2Ftc%2Fpress_room%2Fpress_release_2019%2F201908182.html&d=z%2Bfr9BvhH3rd6UlN4MOb%2FgfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=b42cc5ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.redcross.org.hk/tc/press_room/press_release_2019/201908182.html</a><br />\n8. <span style=\"color: gold;\">國際培幼會</span><br />\n（2017年總收入近8000萬）：無回應，平行時空<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n二.）本地文宣上，各區連儂牆近日被大肆清拆，各位香港人可以喺朝早人多時份重建連儂牆<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n三.）持續喺國際文宣上着力（Twitter, FB, IG），呼籲國際社會支持香港示威者五大訴求，順便將黑警惡行/ 中共建政70年嚟種種歷史惡行公諸於世"},{"pid":"a41e973c5af3a5abd5f65ba0526be10f07a945d1","tid":1748444,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T16:34:59.000Z","msg":"裝修<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13fe7a482646b67c75c6b64c353f77918388378f","tid":1748444,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5603fb3b3c3309ce1345ace85f1dc4